Limo & Limousine Service | Temecula, Riverside & Orange County.

Affordable Limousines is a premier ground transportation service company, providing limousines; SUV limousines, stretch limousines, and Town Car sedans. We also specialize in Wedding Limousines, Proms, Concerts, Funerals, Birthdays, Anniversaries, Homecoming Dances, Business Luncheons, Christmas Parties, Corporate Events, Temecula Wine Tasting Tours, Romantic Getaways, Sporting Events and evening parties
